{{! This handlebar is designed to convert Spells exported from Foundry.  It relies on two modules, PF2E Exporter and More Handlebars Helpers.}}
---
obsidianUIMode: preview
title: "{{{name}}}"
noteType: pf2eSpell
cssclasses: pf2e,pf2e-spell
tags:
  - spell/level/{{system.level.value}}
  {{#each system.traits.value}}
  - trait/{{this}}
   {{/each}}
  - trait/{{system.traits.rarity}}
{{#if system.ritual}}
  - ritual
{{/if~}}
{{#if system.publication.remaster}}
  - remaster
{{/if~}}
aliases: "{{{uuid}}}" 
---
# {{{name}}} {{#if actionGlyph}} {{{ more-handlebars-helpers-table system.time.value "1" "`pf2:1`" "2" "`pf2:2`" "3" "`pf2:3`" "reaction" "`pf2:r`" "free" "`pf2:0`" "1 to 2" "`pf2:1` to `pf2:2`" "1 to 3" "`pf2:1` to `pf2:3`"}}}{{/if}}  
## {{#if isRitual}}Ritual{{else}}{{#if isCantrip}}Cantrip{{else}}{{#if isFocusSpell}}Focus{{else}}Spell{{/if}}{{/if}}{{/if}} {{system.level.value}}
### {{{ more-handlebars-helpers-table system.traits.rarity "common" "" "uncommon" "[uncommon](uncommon \"Uncommon Rarity Trait\")" "rare" "[rare](rare \"Rare Rarity Trait\")" "unique" "[unique](unique \"Unique Rarity Trait\")"}}}
{{~#each system.traits.value}}
[[{{this}}]]{{/each}}
{{#if system.traits.traditions}}**Traditions** {{#each system.traits.traditions}}[[{{this}}]]{{ifThen @last "" ", "}}{{/each}}{{/if}}
{{#unless actionGlyph}}**Cast** {{{ more-handlebars-helpers-table system.time.value "1" "`pf2:1`" "2" "`pf2:2`" "3" "`pf2:3`" "reaction" "`pf2:r`" "free" "`pf2:0`"}}}{{/unless}}
{{~#if system.ritual.secondary.casters~}}
; **Secondary Casters** {{system.ritual.secondary.casters}}
{{/if~}}

{{#if system.cost.value~}}
**Cost** {{{system.cost.value}}}
{{/if~}}

{{#if system.ritual.primary.check~}}
**Primary Check** {{system.ritual.primary.check}}
{{/if~}}

{{#if system.ritual.secondary.checks~}}
**Secondary Checks** {{system.ritual.secondary.checks}}
{{/if~}}

{{#if system.range.value~}}
**Range** {{system.range.value}}
{{/if~}}

{{#if system.area~}}
**Area** {{system.area.value}}-foot {{system.area.type}}
{{/if~}}

{{#if system.target.value~}}
**Targets** {{system.target.value}}
{{/if~}}

{{#if system.defense.save}}
**Saving Throw** {{#if system.defense.save.basic}}basic{{/if}} {{system.defense.save.statistic}}
{{/if~}}

{{#if system.duration.value}}
**Duration** {{system.duration.value}}
{{/if}}
